!Import .merely

# See the HoTT book
# https://hott.github.io/book/hott-online-1353-g16a4bfa.pdf
# p. 131, section 3.8 "Sets and logic" -> "The axiom of choice"

!Axiom AOC: \forall X in U_0. \forall A in (X -> U_0). \forall P in (\forall x in X. A x -> U_0).
    (\forall x in X. Merely (\exists a in A x. P x a)) ->
    Merely (\exists g in (\forall x in X. A x). \forall x in X. P x (g x));
